description: *OFFER ACCEPTED, OPEN HOUSES CANCELLED*  Affordable condo alternative! We invite you to view this amazing 2bd/2.5ba single family row-home located on quiet side street. This 1168 sqft 3-story home with Cen AC has just been freshly painted throughout. On the lower-level you will find a large eat-in kitchen with granite counter-tops & stainless steel appliances as well as a half bath/laundry room. The bright and sunny entry level living room is a adjacent to 2nd bedroom with ensuite bathroom. The entire airy, top floor is dedicated to the primary suite which boast a spacious bathroom and walk-in closet. Enjoy warm summer evenings grilling from your rear patio. Just a short-walk to the many trendy stores and restaurants on W. Broadway such as Capo, Lincoln Tavern and Loco Taqueria & Oyster Bar. Just over a 10min walk to the Broadway T-stop and a short drive to I-93 with easy connections to north and south of the city.
